1
00:00:01,042 --> 00:00:02,959
They were three when we arrived

2
00:00:04,125 --> 00:00:06,042
They tie your hands like this with a plastic strip

3
00:00:06,751 --> 00:00:08,209
And one of them holds you from here

4
00:00:08,542 --> 00:00:10,584
And drags you behind him

5
00:00:11,250 --> 00:00:12,751
When we came, we entered from here

6
00:00:15,417 --> 00:00:20,417
When we arrived, one of them was sitting in this room

7
00:00:21,709 --> 00:00:24,083
It was for reception, he only records your name

8
00:00:25,709 --> 00:00:29,042
He records your full name and your date of birth

9
00:00:29,834 --> 00:00:32,876
And they take you inside to a room for interrogation

10
00:00:34,125 --> 00:00:35,709
And the interrogation starts inside

11
00:00:36,709 --> 00:00:38,334
Honestly, when you enter here

12
00:00:39,626 --> 00:00:43,500
When you see their looks, you lower your eyes out of fear

13
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,334
Because of fear, you can’t look at them

14
00:00:47,792 --> 00:00:50,667
And this was real

15
00:00:51,334 --> 00:00:52,709
We really feared them

16
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:58,459
There were many of them, spread out here, not just one or two

17
00:00:59,167 --> 00:01:00,626
They were present in large numbers

18
00:01:01,459 --> 00:01:05,834
Every moment one comes in, five go out, four enter, and so on

19
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:09,459
But from fear, you can’t look at them

20
00:01:10,584 --> 00:01:12,042
And you can’t talk to them

21
00:01:13,250 --> 00:01:16,792
When they question you inside during interrogation

22
00:01:17,792 --> 00:01:19,626
You answer with just one word

23
00:01:20,083 --> 00:01:22,083
If you answer with more than one word

24
00:01:23,626 --> 00:01:27,542
He silences you, and God alone knows what
he’ll do to you, they don’t accept that

25
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:33,792
And out of fear, you answer him while trembling
